Subject: Upgrading to the latest version Netwrix Enterprise Auditor
Description:
Hello, 
I would like to upgrade the version of Netwrix Enterprise Auditor,  Netwrix Access Information Center, Netwrix Active Monitor, Netwrix Sensitive Data Discovery to the latest version. 

Thank you,
Bao Luu.
Next_Steps__c: Awaiting next job runs to ID any issues.
Solution_Comment__c:
Upgraded the current version of Stealth application(s) running in the Environment:

FROM:
Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA)              11.6.0.69
NEA Access Information (AIC)                  11.6.0.12
NEA Sensitive Data (SDD)                         11.6.0.11

TO:
Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA)              11.6.0.117
NEA Access Information (AIC)                  11.6.0.25
NEA Sensitive Data (SDD)                         11.6.0.13

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor vl1.6 > Installation > Installation & Configuration Overview > Enterprise Auditor Console Upgrade
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Install/Application/Upgrade/Overview.htm

Netwrix Access Information Center 11.6 > Installation Overview > Upgrade Procedure https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/AIC_11.6/page/Content/Access/InformationCenter/Installation/Upgrade.htm

We added a Weekly Schedule tasks for the AD Activity job other than on Thursday when it will run in concession with the Overall AD job group.
